'''Buldobeasts''' were creatures found on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Vryssa]].

[[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Scout trooper/Legends|scout troopers]] patrolling the Vryssa garrison once spotted something moving in the nearby [[Tree/Legends|trees]]. Thinking it was just a buldobeast, only one trooper set out to investigate. What the trooper thought was a buldobeast was actually [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]]. Fett killed the trooper with ease.

